":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T00:17:33.000Z","msg":"人大釋法唔係釋基本法，而係釋宣誓條例就無破壞法治，相反俾人恰到上心口走出去反抗就係向法院施壓=破壞法治？<br />\n呢篇野真係痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb7cdd53b86c4ee785b0185a0000c0dba4d43c5e","tid":327517,"uid":82935,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T00:25:36.000Z","msg":"其實民主派仲有一招, <br />\n只要搵人陪幾個民選建制派走狗 坐洗頭艇 去效遊. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁咪可以平衡番 議會人數 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利伸: 係 共產黨  同 吳亮星 教我既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"554e4a33d7ff1322e7ca701d9c43fd2cd4a82e9c","tid":327517,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T00:27:40.000Z","msg":"DQ咗6人後 <br />\n泛民已失去分組點票否決權<br />\n(預計補選會失去至少2席 仍然失否決權) <br />\n而補選準備工作通常需要4-6月時間<br />\n係呢個時期<br />\n建制派可以修改議事規則<br />\n例如限制議員發言次數及時間<br />\n以後無得拉布 <br />\n發言完坐低等例行性投票"},{"pid":"076d2ad667ac274b29ec3c5b7e716ce126ff4366","tid":327517,"uid":21772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T00:32:23.000Z","msg":"DQ之前有擋過咩撥款咁撚巴閉"},{"pid":"f513f8bd445f4a48555c9282138e630f609152b1","tid":327517,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T03:39:46.000Z","msg":"冇糧出就梗係唔可行啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be859d7bcfadaa77eca72b946830f04835827e3b","tid":327517,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T03:41:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當年蘋果跟民主黨一齊反對五區公投</blockquote><br />\n最後五區公投完全冇用,投票率極低冇指標性"},{"pid":"fa20e2e66e4d938ae1b44bd9accaa19b24743808","tid":327517,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T03:42:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"59fa7952d1ae9dd798bf98ec5c5ce07c6deb799a","tid":327517,"uid":281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T03:44:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid"